  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give an education to 100 teenage mothers in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Due to the COVID-19 pandemic resulting in closure of schools, lots of school going girls in rural Ghana have become pregnant and if nothing is done immediately to send them back to school, they would be married off and have their lives destroyed. This project seeks to support 100 teenage mothers in rural Ghana go back to school to acquire secondary or vocational/technical education. The project will give scholarships to these girls to enable them go back and stay in school till completion.</narrative>
  </description>
